---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Meter 5G Gateway | Blue Cap IT — Meter Partner" description="Meter's 5G Gateway provides cellular ISP failover, out-of-band management, and up to 1200Mbps throughput over 5G. Keep your network online even when your primary ISP goes down.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/meter/Meter-purple.png" alt="Meter" style="max-height:60px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="meter.html">Networking</a> <span>/</span> 5G Gateway</div>
      <div class="section-label">Meter Hardware</div>
      <h1>Meter <span class="grad">5G Gateway</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Never lose connectivity again. The Meter Gateway delivers up to 1200Mbps over 5G, providing automatic ISP failover, out-of-band management, and backup connectivity for your most critical locations — even in harsh, rugged environments.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GATEWAY FEATURES -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <img src="/meter/hw-p-series.avif" alt="Meter 5G Gateway" style="width:100%;max-width:500px;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;" />
          <div class="section-label">G-Series Gateway</div>
          <h2>Always-On <span class="grad">Connectivity.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">When your primary ISP goes down, the Meter Gateway automatically kicks in over 5G cellular — keeping your business connected, your devices online, and your operations running. It also provides out-of-band management, so Meter can remotely access and troubleshoot your network even when the primary internet connection is unavailable.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📡</div>
            <div><h4>5G Cellular Connectivity</h4><p>Up to 1200Mbps throughput over 5G. Fast enough to keep your business running at full speed even without a wired ISP connection.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔄</div>
            <div><h4>Automatic ISP Failover</h4><p>When your primary internet goes down, the Gateway detects the outage and switches to 5G automatically — no manual intervention, no downtime.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔧</div>
            <div><h4>Out-of-Band Management</h4><p>Meter can remotely access, diagnose, and fix your network over the cellular connection — even when your main internet is completely offline.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🏔️</div>
            <div><h4>Rugged &amp; Reliable</h4><p>Built to operate in harsh and rugged environments. The Gateway is designed for remote sites, construction locations, warehouses, and outdoor deployments.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- USE CASES -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Use Cases</div>
        <h2>Where the Gateway <span class="grad">Shines</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">The Meter Gateway is ideal for any location where reliable connectivity is critical — or where wired internet simply isn't available.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🏢</div>
          <h3>Primary ISP Backup</h3>
          <p>Add a 5G backup to any office or facility. If your wired ISP goes down, the Gateway keeps your business online automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3>Remote &amp; Temporary Sites</h3>
          <p>Construction sites, pop-up locations, and temporary offices where running fiber isn't practical. Get enterprise networking over 5G.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🏭</div>
          <h3>Warehouses &amp; Facilities</h3>
          <p>Large facilities where wired connectivity is unreliable or expensive to extend. The Gateway provides coverage where cables can't reach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🏪</div>
          <h3>Retail &amp; Branch Offices</h3>
          <p>Multi-location businesses that need guaranteed uptime at every site. Keep point-of-sale, security cameras, and operations running 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Never Go Offline <span class="grad">Again</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to add 5G failover to your network. We'll assess your connectivity needs and design a solution that keeps you online no matter what.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
